text: Manon Jutras (born 25 November 1967) is a road cyclist from Canada. She represented her nation at the 2004 Summer Olympics. She also rode at the 2003 and 2004 UCI Road World Championships. ==References== ==External links== * profile at Procyclingstats.com Category:1967 births Category:Canadian female cyclists Category:Living people Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Cyclists at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic cyclists of Canada
